{"data": [{"id": "4743577", "title": "Verizon: Narrow Margin Of Safety Per Graham P/E And Number", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Verizon\" data-id=\"1460144578\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>VZ stock: previous thesis and Q3 earnings</h2> <p>My <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4727472-verizon-q3-preview-you-want-total-shareholder-yield-not-dividend-yield\">last coverage</a> on Verizon stock (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VZ\" title=\"Verizon Communications Inc.\">VZ</a></span>) was a preview of its FY Q3 2024 earnings report (\u201cER\u201d). That article was titled \"Verizon Q3 Preview: You Want Total Shareholder Yield, Not Dividend Yield\u201d and was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1460144578/image_1460144578.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743577-verizon-narrow-margin-of-safety-per-graham-pe-and-number", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 18:04:58"}, {"id": "4743576", "title": "Zeta Global: A Value Play Post Omnicom-Interpublic Merger", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Data analytics automated with AI technology. Big data, business analytics and artificial intelligence automation. Dashboard report with sales and operations charts and KPI insights on touch screen.\" data-id=\"2096475191\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NicoElNino</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Last July, I initiated my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4708386-zeta-global-a-unique-value-proposition-in-the-martech-industry\">coverage</a> on Zeta Global Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZETA\" title=\"Zeta Global Holdings Corp.\">ZETA</a></span>) with a buy rating due to its unified MarTech platform that could help it continue growing rapidly in the coming years. While the stock has reached</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743576-zeta-global-value-play-post-omnicom-interpublic-merger", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 18:00:57"}, {"id": "4743571", "title": "AMD Is Back In The Buy Zone (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AMD headquarters in Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1679336666\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>In light of its <a href=\"https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_9dbb409594957336af50b3d0d14cd8bd/amd/news/2024-10-29_AMD_Reports_Third_Quarter_2024_Financial_1224.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Q3 2024 report</a>, I downgraded semiconductor giant <b>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMD\" title=\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\">AMD</a></span>) stock to a \"Hold\" rating, citing its inadequate long-term risk/reward:</p> <blockquote> <p><em>In Q3, AMD beat consensus estimates but failed to deliver superlative guidance. As I</em></p> </blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743571-amd-is-back-in-the-buy-zone-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:53:39"}, {"id": "4743588", "title": "Communications Services Leads U.S. Equity Sectors In 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesswoman checking app on smart phone while working on web design in studio\" data-id=\"1139932722\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The neck-and-neck horse race for first place among equity sectors has recently given way to a decisive lead for communications services stocks year to date, based on a set of ETFs through Tuesday's close (Dec. 10).</p> <p>As <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4736378-communications-financials-take-lead-top-sector-performers\" rel=\"noopener noopener\">previously</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743588-communications-services-leads-us-equity-sectors-in-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:50:00"}, {"id": "4743587", "title": "Allspring Small Company Value Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Franchise business growth with earning money, copy space.\" data-id=\"1287899462\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"845px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">oatawa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Quarterly review</h2> <p>The Allspring Small Company Value Fund underperformed the benchmark for the quarter. The materials, consumer staples, and health care sectors were the primary contributors to performance, while the energy, communication services, and financials sectors detracted from performance.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743587-allspring-small-company-value-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:40:00"}, {"id": "4743569", "title": "Slash Your 2024 Tax Bill With These Tax-Loss Stocks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stock Market Crash and Escape - Global Business Strategy Exchange\" data-id=\"1200508619\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8000px\" height=\"5000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sefa ozel</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With only two trading weeks left, investors should consider booking losses <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743013-tax-loss-stocks-to-sell-before-everyone-else-does\">now before the crowd does</a>. The risk of getting ahead of the market is that those tax-loss candidates may rise within the 30-day wash rule.</p> <p>One</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743569-slash-your-2024-tax-bill-with-these-tax-loss-stocks", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:35:32"}, {"id": "4743566", "title": "JPRE: Current Allocation Suggests Defensive 2025 Positioning", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"JP Morgan in Hong Kong\" data-id=\"1389125589\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">winhorse</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The JPMorgan Realty Income ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JPRE\" title=\"JPMorgan Realty Income ETF\">JPRE</a></span>) has marginally outperformed the Vanguard Real Estate Index Fund ETF (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>) so far in 2024, delivering a ~12% total return against the ~10% gain for the broad U.S. real estate ETF:</p> <p></p> <p>After</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743566-jpre-current-allocation-suggests-defensive-2025-positioning", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:26:12"}, {"id": "4743565", "title": "Avidity Biosciences Advances With FDA Clearance And Promising Data For Rare Diseases", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mecanismo de los conjugados anticuerpo-oligonucle\u00f3tido o AOC\" data-id=\"1826415391\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.co